-- China, Russia Main Sponsors of Spying on German Companies, Die Welt Says
-- Andreas Cremer
-- 2010-06-22T05:26:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/china-russia-main-sponsors-of-spying-on-german-companies-die-welt-says.html

          
          
             China and Russia are the main
sponsors of Web-based industrial espionage against German
companies and state agencies,  Die Welt  reported.  
 Chinese and Russian intelligence services are mainly
seeking technical information and corporate strategies, the
newspaper said, citing a report by the German government on the
protection of the constitution.  
 To contact the reporters on this story:
